But whatever you think of Rockstar’s approach to the material, it’s difficult to fault its hard work. For previous GTA games, it has flown teams of designers from Edinburgh to Miami and New York to take hours of video and sound tape, analyse traffic patterns and consult with ex-gangsters, mafiosi and law enforcement officers.
